issued a permit for the event but emphasized they were not 
endorsing it 
possession of small amounts of marijuana in ann arbor is 
punishable by a 5 fine 
ive been coming to this since i was a little boy said a 
29yearold who called himself jizmo noodles and was one of the 
first to light up my first one was in 1973 its a means of 
expression civil disobedience 
