<TEXT>
when the clock jumps forward an hour for 
daylightsaving time at 2 am sunday morning it means a little 
more than a lost hour of sleep 
peoples stomachs will be telling them snickers bar and 
well be serving lunch but if youre an early eater itll be 
beneficial said jeff manzer manager of the chattanooga 
riverboat company 
the firm plans to serve an easter brunch on the tennessee river 
sunday afternoon but the time change will probably affect 
peoples appetites said manzer 
businesses and services that work on into the night lost an hour 
or gained an hour depending on the point of view 
some police officers who work the night shift get to go home an 
hour early they dont lose an hours pay for their early 
departure and when the time changes back in the fall theyll get 
an hours overtime pay officials said friday 
firefighters who work 24hour shifts are in the same situation 
some churches will hold additional services for sleepyheads and 
for the holiday crowds 
going visiting for easter the nations public transportation 
system is ready for the switch said fred waymack manager of a 
